                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7525" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0242</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2339 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乘势而上开新局：信息化助力C中心内控管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Take Advantage of the Situation to Create a New Situation: IT-enabled Internal Control Management of C Center</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈秀秀，高雨婷，黄艺娟，汪洋，卓林全</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建省残疾人体育运动管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行政事业单位；内部控制；风险管理；信息系统</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Administrative Institutions；Internal Control；Risk Management； Information System</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制体系是行政事业单位有效防范化解风险、提高机构运行效率的重要手段，也是扎实推进国家治理能力现代化的保障机制，而信息化建设是保障内部控制体系落地的重要途径。本案例阐述了福建省残疾人体育运动管理中心为了提升内部治理水平所开展的建设单位内部控制系统的一系列过程，重点分析了中心所面临的单位和业务层面的内部控制风险，以及内部控制信息系统的作用流程。本案例旨在帮助学生理解行政事业单位内部控制理论、风险管理以及信息系统的赋能作用，引导学生总结出完善企事业单位内部控制体系的经验，实现其内部智慧治理，提高服务质量，充分展现其社会职能。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Internal control system is an important means for administrative institutions to effectively prevent risks, improve the efficiency of institutional operation, and therefore promote the modernization of national governance capacity solidly. Informazation construction is an important way to ensure the implementation of the internal control system. This case describes a series of processes in which Fujian Provincial Disability Sports Management Center carries out the construction of the unit&#39;s internal control system in order to improve the level of internal governance. It focuses on analyzing the internal control risks faced by the center at the unit and business levels, as well as the function process of the internal control information system. This case aims to help students to understand the internal control theory of administrative institutions, risk management and the enabling role of information systems, guide students to think critically about the experience of internal control system construction of enterprises and institutions in order to realize their internal intelligent governance, improve service quality, and fully demonstrate their social functions.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《管理信息系统》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息化建设的驱动因素；COSO内部控制理论；风险管理理论；内部控制与风险管理的关系</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
